{"tid":316634,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工搭車坐低都比廢老串","createTime":"2017-07-11T01:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T03:20:05.000Z","uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e32582db8760c852e3e688deb243e87c4ba7680","tid":316634,"uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T01:13:13.000Z","msg":"今朝一上車見到兩隻廢老坐係關愛座，咁我就坐落隔離。<br />\n<br />\n隨後就聽到兩隻廢老(一雄一雌)係度講野，一開始我都不而為然，一隻廢老傾電話都可以全車箱聽到，兩隻廢老嘈就一定啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但焗住聽之下，聽到隻雄性廢老講咩「一個屎忽坐落黎」，「後生就企係度當做運動啦」，「廢事同佢爭」。原來佢想移過黎唔坐關愛座。撚知佢坐落去又想郁黎郁去咩。個雌性廢老重好得戚話「係啊，佢地唔敢坐關愛座架」。最後我望實我隔離個雄性廢老，佢擰開塊面又開始講其他野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以後搭車唔單止要睇廢老坐左未，重要睇埋坐左既廢老動向。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a851cb490be3a653670b5cf3a0c21f7f0dbe2d3","tid":316634,"uid":49815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T01:25:24.000Z","msg":"關愛座係留翻比你地啲老骨頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f3922dce70df14e94e29748c78bbbf2b9d8acf","tid":316634,"uid":48277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T01:25:53.000Z","msg":"唔當場屌鳩佢地 而家開post 托呀<br />\nd廢老又唔會上黎睇"},{"pid":"3f6d2085845c585450cb484429d7c5143b2f2ec4","tid":316634,"uid":22453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T01:27:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打擊廢老 人人有責</span>"},{"pid":"f9204399f787f5c50c21af9c367bb3c2a22c577f","tid":316634,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T01:29:30.000Z","msg":"係就當面屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba52b7af096bfcfdf23907285c59b7229f99655","tid":316634,"uid":24698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾廢老阻撚住人返工"},{"pid":"b43aa4a8043b42cc2c4197e489a1c8290a071744","tid":316634,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T01:32:28.000Z","msg":"佢出口，你出手，輸晒啦"},{"pid":"6f1252515b8c0c25edaa4d87c33d9ddf9be7f585","tid":316634,"uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T01:34:18.000Z","msg":"我望得佢就預開拖啦，點知佢淆底唔再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da75c53fdbae4e4eee47cc534599bc7c234693cf","tid":316634,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾廢老阻撚住人返工</blockquote><br />\n繁忙時間唔應該有2蚊優惠"},{"pid":"16e1bf48e57a07f0c1da106d72cb35abc6c4db70","tid":316634,"uid":89416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上車就聽歌<br />\n佢行到過黎我都係會唔理"},{"pid":"ee8579923a357461142afb6a3ed432c206ec64f7","tid":316634,"uid":64155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"屌廢老屎忽啦"}]}